name: Dumble
details: Dumbbells are small bars that fit in your hand and have equal weights on either side.

name: Batting Rope
details: Unilateral waves. Start with your feet hip-width apart, holding one rope in each hand.

name: One-Arm Hang
details: Place a chair at the bottom of a horizontal bar. Stand on the chair with our chin above the bar.

name: Folding Treadmills
details: Treadmill exercising machines are well known and basically consist of a relatively wide endless belt.

name: Yoga
details: To begin meditating, find a place where you can sit comfortably and quietly.

name: Stability Ball
details: Get in a high-plank position with your hands directly underneath your shoulders and your shins on top of a stability ball.
